WEBVTT

1
00:10:20.980 --> 00:10:23.060 
- 麦瑟尔先生 - 这里 就在夹克这里
- Mr. Maisel... -Right there, right on the jacket.

2
00:10:23.080 --> 00:10:24.540 
- 一个手印 不是我的 - 我知道
- A handprint. Not my handprint. - I know.

3
00:10:24.570 --> 00:10:26.580 
但我夹克现在成这样了
But it is my jacket, which is now ruined

4
00:10:26.610 --> 00:10:27.630 
因为这里 左手边
because right there, left hand,

5
00:10:27.660 --> 00:10:29.210 
- 很明显 - 我会查出
- clear as day. - I'll find out...

6
00:10:29.240 --> 00:10:31.340 
我要你找出这个该死的手印是谁弄的
I want you to find out whose goddamn handprint that is,

7
00:10:31.370 --> 00:10:33.870 
然后带过来见我 明白了吗 好吗 好的
and you bring him to me. Yes? Good? Great.

8
00:10:33.990 --> 00:10:35.400 
干的好 女士们
Good work, ladies.

9
00:10:35.420 --> 00:10:37.170 
- 保持下去 - 爸
- Keep 'em hum, hum, humming along. - Pop?

10
00:10:37.190 --> 00:10:39.030 
我就爱听这机器运转的声音
Love to hear the sound of the machines.

11
00:10:39.060 --> 00:10:40.800 
- 你看起来没病啊 - 爸
- You don't look sick. - Pop?

12
00:10:40.820 --> 00:10:42.130 
康复了
Miraculous recovery?

13
00:10:42.150 --> 00:10:44.210 
现代科学的又一大奇迹吗
Modern science score another knockout?

14
00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:46.110 
- 我没病 - 是吗
- I'm not sick. - That's not what I heard.

15
00:10:46.140 --> 00:10:47.720 
可我听说你病了 钉住
I heard you were sick. Pin.

16
00:10:47.750 --> 00:10:48.930 
安静
Quiet.

17
00:10:48.950 --> 00:10:50.230 
亲家母一小时前打电话给我
Mother-in-law called an hour ago,

18
00:10:50.250 --> 00:10:52.400 
说家里每个人都病了 每个人
said everyone in the family is sick. Everyone.

